title: I've Been Holding Back on YouTube... But Not Anymore
description:
I wanted to give a quick update to you on the direction of my channel and my plans to 10x the value of my content for you and your AI journey.

1. I'll be uploading once a week (Wednesdays at 7:00 PM CDT) instead of twice a week now so I can focus more on quality over quantity for my content.

2. I'm going to be leaning more into what makes me stand out - my focus on the higher leverage skills for building AI agents like architecture, system design, best practices for building AI agents, etc. so you truly have what it takes to have a big impact with AI and not just build toys, demos, or simple automations.

I'm super excited for what I have in store! I truly believe my content will simply be better in every way possible.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

If you're looking to join a community for early AI adopters to master AI & AI Agents and transform your career or business, check out Dynamous here:

https://dynamous.ai

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Artificial Intelligence is no doubt the future of not just software development but the whole world. And I'm on a mission to master it - focusing first on mastering AI Agents.

Join me as I push the limits of what is possible with AI. 

I'll be uploading videos weekly Wednesdays at 7:00 PM CDT!
